<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Isaac Pyle Portfolio</title>
  <%- partial('head') %>
</head>

<body>
  <%- partial('navbar') %>
    <!-- MAIN PAGE CONTENT -->
    <div id="main-content">
      <div id="portfolio-header">
        <div id="portfolio-header-image-container">
          <img src="./assets/images/home_screen_img.png" class="portfolio-header-image">
        </div>
        <div id="portfolio-header-text-container">
            <div class="header-text">
              <span class="main-title">Hey, I'm Isaac.</span>
              <div class="body-text">I'm a backend software engineer looking for my next position. 
                As a recent Platform Engineer at Garmin, I have skills in:
                <ul>
                  <li>Java</li>
                  <li>Spring Framework / Spring Boot</li>
                  <li>Kotlin</li>
                  <li>PostgreSQL</li>
                  <li>AWS</li>
                  <li>Docker</li>
                </ul>
                and many other tools.</div>
            </div>
            <a class="button" id="my-work-link">
              <span class="button-text">Check out my projects</span> 
              <image src="./assets/icons/arrow-right.svg" class="right-arrow-icon"/>
            </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ABOUT SECTION -->
      <div id="about-section">
        <span class="subheader-text">About Me</span>
        <div class="about-section-content">
          <div class="body-text">I graduated cum laude from the <a class="text-link" href="https://www.colorado.edu" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">University of Colorado - Boulder</a> 
            in May of 2022 with a degree in Computer Science from the Engineering Department. 
            Some of my recent classes were 'Object Oriented Programming' and 'Software Development Methods and Tools', 
            which prepared me appropriately for a position at <a class="text-link" href="https://www.garmin.com/en-US/garmin-pay/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Garmin International</a> 
            working on the Garmin Pay Platform team. Here, I developed skills in Java, Kotlin, AWS, Docker, and others, but focused primarily on Java.
          </div>
          <div class="body-text">More specifically, I quickly got up to speed using Spring and Spring boot to build and maintain 
            RESTful APIs which are the backbone of the platform. It has a distributed microservice architecture running in docker containers,
            and these talk using RabbitMQ as the messaging broker. </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- PROJECTS / MY WORK SECTION -->
      <a id="my-work-section-anchor"></a>
      <div id="my-work-section">
        <span class="subheader-text">Projects</span>
        <div class="projects-container">

          <div class="project-card">
            <a href="./fintrack-project.html"><img src="./assets/images/sql_diagram.png" class="project-image"></a>
            <div class="project-card-text-container">
              <div class="subheader-text project-title">FinTrack Backend App</div>
              <div class="body-text project-card-text">The backend for a finance tracking application, using Java, Spring Boot and PostgreSQL.</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <a class="button" href="https://github.com/IsaacPyle/FinTrack" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">
                <span class="button-text">GitHub</span>
                <image src="./assets/icons/arrow-right.svg" class="right-arrow-icon"/>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="project-card">
            <a href="./chess-project.html"><img src="./assets/images/chess_board.png" class="project-image"></a>
            <div class="project-card-text-container">
              <div class="subheader-text project-title">A Game of Chess</div>
              <div class="body-text project-card-text">Designed and developed a Python game of chess, in which the opponent moves randomly in order to simulate a real game of chess.</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <a class="button" href="https://github.com/IsaacPyle/chess-bot" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">
                <span class="button-text">GitHub</span>
                <image src="./assets/icons/arrow-right.svg" class="right-arrow-icon"/>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="project-card">
            <a href="./portfolio-project.html"><img src="./assets/images/portfolio_project_img.png" class="project-image"></a>
            <div class="project-card-text-container">
              <div class="subheader-text project-title">This Portfolio Website</div>
              <div class="body-text project-card-text">Built this website to display my projects using HTML, CSS and EJS. Hosted on GitHub Pages using Harp to compile EJS to HTML.</div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <a class="button" href="https://github.com/IsaacPyle/portfolio" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">
                <span class="button-text">GitHub</span>
                <image src="./assets/icons/arrow-right.svg" class="right-arrow-icon"/>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%- partial('footer') %>
  </body>
</html>